Greetings from Los Angeles, where I=E2=80=99m back at home after a
one-night mandatory evacuation. Welcome back to In the Room. This has been =
a surreal few days, to say the least, and I=E2=80=99m grateful to all of yo=
u who have reached out over the last 48 hours. And, once again, immense tha=
nks to all the incredible reporters and production crews who have been on t=
he front lines=E2=80=94and, of course, the firefighters.

=C2=A0

In tonight=E2=80=99s email, my partner Tara Palmeri
assesses the implications of the impending TikTok ban, which the Supreme Co=
