ment question. Instead, he writes that the court should =E2=80=9Cstay the s=
tatute=E2=80=99s effective date=E2=80=9D to =E2=80=9Callow his incoming Adm=
inistration to pursue a negotiated resolution.=E2=80=9D In other words: <em=
>I alone can fix it.</em></p></div>
